{"tid":1730833,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"trigger九龍西以外既金鋪同銀行警鐘","createTime":"2019-11-17T14:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T16:37:09.000Z","uid":76310,"like":35,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"231ffb53bbd102f290b01512f17d21f0693bd7e2","tid":1730833,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"❗️❗️❗️❗️今晚幫poly既方法係trigger九龍西以外既金鋪同銀行警鐘❗️❗️❗️❗️<br />\n<br />\n有朋友知道今晚班狗步署<br />\n其他區既狗已經借哂防暴比九龍西既commander 佢地今晚一定要搞掂poly<br />\n要幫poly唔係係九龍西開花 係響九龍西以外既地方開花 務求要班狗call番自己team既人番黎先可以疏散到係poly既警力<br />\n最快既方法係打爆金鋪銀行 因為直接trigger到警鐘<br />\n要直接trigger到警鐘❗️❗️<br />\n要係九龍西以外❗️❗️"},{"pid":"36380230f16646e49f7ef79335801c62e697975c","tid":1730833,"uid":215287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"係poly附近大廈既手足，唔洗真係放火，打爆個火警鐘就可以幫到手，我做保安，個火警鐘響左，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保安係停唔到響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一定要消防來到用佢條匙先停到，一響大把街坊落街，求附近手足幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal